Sentencas: Crystal structure, thermogravimetry (TG), thermal expansion coefficient (TEC), electrical conductivity and AC impedance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(1-x)LaxCo0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSLCF; 0.05 <= x <= 0.20) were studied in relation to their potential use as intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) cathode.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: A single cubic pervoskite was observed by X-ray diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The TEC of BSLCF was increasing slightly with the increasing content of La, and all the compounds showed abnormal expansion at high temperature.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Proved by the TG result, it was associated with the loss of lattice oxygen.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity, which is the main defect of Ba0.5Sr0.5 Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF), was improved by La doping, e.g., the compound of x = 0.20 demonstrated a conductivity of sigma = 376 S cm(-1) at 392 degrees C.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The increase of electrical conductivity resulted from the increased concentration of charge carrier induced by La doping.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: In addition, the AC impedance revealed the better electrochemical performance of BSLCF.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: For example, at 500 degrees C, the sample with composition x = 0.15 yielded the resistance values of 2.12 Omega cm(2), which was only 46% of BSCF.
Titulo: Thermal, electrical, and electrochemical properties of Lanthanum-doped Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ
